message:
Determine which eyebrow is more dominant. Before beginning your training, you will want to figure out which eyebrow will be most easily trained. Typically, this will be your dominant eyebrow. Stand in front of a mirror, and try to lift your right eyebrow. Then try to lift only your left eyebrow.

IMPORTANT: Determine which eyebrow is more dominant. Before beginning your training, you will want to figure out which eyebrow will be most easily trained.
